{"type": "article", "id": 13994, "title": "咽喉灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-26T07:50:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143136dVx0CFPyEwHgmqUM.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些看上去像是通风管的东西其实是来自 Keha3 的一系列灯具，他们叫做“咽喉灯”，借通风管的形状给灯带来非常强的灵活性，几乎可以任意调整灯的角度，为不同的方向带去照明。而且不同的长度也可以满足多种情形下的使用需求。不过这种风格的灯具也许很难找到相匹配风格的装修风格，也许脱离家居，对于工业化风格的环境是最合适的。<a href=\"http://keha3.ee/en/indoor-lighting/throat-lamp/%E2%80%8B\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141640oKefyXYAmiuvtTg6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141641tfdbo6BAGi7pVJOU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66469428\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141641RU5dIjm7rNsgHqQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416420GqnV2stcIp7RfuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416439TOMq4GnQNUDlXiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141643cKDhskeF2RS3vYC8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141644dB4s1NXGm3KDRFiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.35138889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}